						               													<description>THE BATTLE OF MARDAVHAIN - COLLECTIBLE CARD GAME&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During the game, players can embark on a journey to the ancient land of Mardavhain, where peace has been disturbed by evil forces, and battles have been raging ever since. Become the strongest and rule the land!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;DIFFERENT MODES&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Choose which deck you want to play with. Will you play with the basic deck, a shared deck with your friends, or will you play with your own deck?&amp;#10;     Choose your game mode. In each round, you can draw new character cards, or you can play in survival mode, where each player has a set number of cards, and there are no additional card draws&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;HOW TO PLAY:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     2-4 players can play on the game board.&amp;#10;     You need to occupy territory from the other players. At the beginning of the game, strategy is important because you need to place character cards for defense and action cards that other players cannot see. Then, the battle for territory begins. The outcome of the battle is decided based on the character cards' health points, attack and defense values, using dice.&amp;#10;     The winner is the one who holds the most or even all the territories.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;HOW TO WIN&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game lasts until all the character cards from the deck are used up. The player with the most territories wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;SURVIVOR MODE:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     In this game mode, the setup is the same as in the regular game, but after battles, players cannot draw new character cards. They must continue to play with the cards they used for the attacks.&amp;#10;     In this case, the HP value of the character cards that participated in battle remains the same, and players must continue to fight with these cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
